  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list>
<item>Model a wave, moving with a constant wave velocity, with a mathematical expression</item>
<item>Calculate the velocity and acceleration of the medium</item>
<item>Show how the velocity of the medium differs from the wave velocity (propagation velocity)</item>
</list></md:abstract>
